  "rationale": "Repair note: the prior render KeyError:'body' came from a block slot whose copy object omitted a required sub-slot; this pass composes with flat primitive slots (heading/paragraph/eyebrow/link/image/quote/caption/feature-item/list) so every copy shape matches its contract, and the About/Heritage 'body' role is now an explicit paragraph slot. Order follows the one-scroll brief: an inverse hero bookend carries the ONLY accent on its didone display title over full-bleed timber photography (sanctioned text-on-media + media-over-media overlap + stagger). Every subsequent section is primary/panel with no accent to satisfy single-accent. About and Visit reuse the anchored-statement split; Gallery reuses the full-bleed counter-band with a static counter and marginal caption; the Curator quote reuses the portrait collage. Heritage is the required novel off-grid section: a ghost '1941 / 2023' watermark behind a heavily staggered timeline built from a single repeatable feature-item run \u2014 a structure the seed library lacked but the brief's heritage timeline implies. Newsletter uses underline-only inline submit (no boxed input, no button); footer is slash-nav + socials as open lists."
